#Text=Australian Stingers stung by US at FINA World League Final gold medal match
#Text=Sunday , June 3 , 2012
#Text=( 6 ) Bronwen Knox during a test match between Great Britain and Australia earlier in the year Image : Laura Hale .

#Text=In the gold medal match at water polo 's FINA World League Final tonight between the Australia Stingers and United States women 's national water polo team , Australia lost 4 – 6 to the USA in the last major competition before the 2012 Summer Olympics .
#Text=The victory made for seven World League Super Final titles for Team USA .
#Text=At 7:00 p.m.
#Text=Chinese local time , 9:00 p.m.
#Text=Australian local time , the game got under way , with a Tweet from Australian Water Polo for fans at home who could not watch the game live .
#Text=The Australians were down at quarter time , 1 – 2 with the team 's only goal coming from Bronwen Knox off a pass by Kate Gynther .
#Text=By half time , Australia had battled back to take the lead 4 – 3 , only to finish the third period tied 4 – 4 with the United States , and eventually lose 4 – 6 .
#Text=In the lead up to the World League Final , the Australians spent time in Singapore before departing for China .
#Text=While in Singapore , players had an opportunity to relax at the pool and several , including Knox , Rowena Webster , Nicola Zagame , and Melissa Rippon were very active on Twitter .
#Text=The team arrived in Shanghai and the Shanghai Institute of Sport a week before the start of the FINA Super League Finals .
#Text=During their week-long preparation , they worked on strength and fitness training .
#Text=When away from the pool , they did not have access to Twitter , Facebook , or television and had to entertain themselves using other means .
#Text=Players finally explored the city six days after their arrival .
#Text=Australian assistant coach Ryan Moar in Canberra Image : Bidgee .
#Text=With limited opportunities for amusement in the hotel room during the competition , assistant coach Ryan Moar updated his Twitter account and played with a toy helicopter .
#Text=Several of the players who were active on Twitter before departing for China stopped updating , including Webster , Rippon , and Zagame .
#Text=Knox and Moran continued to provide updates on Twitter and Instagram throughout the competition .
#Text=Australian game days during the tournament included warming up poolside before the start of their games , and cooling down in the pool after them .
#Text=Going into their match against the USA , they notched an 8 – 7 victory over China , an 18 to nil victory against Germany , and a 9 – 7 overtime shootout win against Russia .
#Text=On gold medal game day , Jane Moran updated her Twitter account to say " Final of World League Super Finals today v USA - goooo Stingers ! ‪#stingerspride " .
#Text=About eight hours prior to game time , the team finished their final training session .
#Text=Earlier in the afternoon , prior to game time in Australia , Channel 9 ran a feature on the team .
#Text=Prior to the start of the game , the Australian Stingers official team Twitter account mocked Team USA for their team-branded k tape .
#Text=During the pre-game warm up , team members did a variety of things including playing with their phones , warming up , and getting their arms taped .
#Text=It was business as usual for the team that had beaten the United States the previous month at the VISA Water Polo International .

#Text=The bronze medal match between the China women 's national water polo team and Greece women 's national water polo team preceded the gold medal game , which Greece won 8 – 7 , with quarter scoring of 1 – 2 in the first , 4 – 2 in the second , 1 – 2 in the third , and 1 – 2 in the fourth .
#Text=In the other match , the Russia women 's national water polo team easily beat the Germany women 's national water polo team 18-4 .
